headlines.description: Angel Rodriguez hit a clutch 3-pointer with 1:12 left to play as Miami, which blew a 21-point lead in the second half, held off Wichita State to advance to the Sweet 16.
headlines.shortLinkText: Rodriguez rescues Canes after Wichita State rally
